{"tid":2031280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國駐意大利大使李軍華：中國人不是「戰狼」，而是「功夫熊貓」","createTime":"2020-05-23T09:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T12:43:28.000Z","uid":48040,"like":61,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"82cc62aad50b21f365306cb269f4240eb6bae29d","tid":2031280,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:52:03.000Z","msg":"《中國是&ldquo;戰狼式&rdquo;外交？駐意大使：&ldquo;功夫熊貓&rdquo;比喻更貼切》<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ifeng.com/c/7weDD0ptS1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ifeng.com%2Fc%2F7weDD0ptS1Q&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=2e5cd4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ifeng.com/c/7weDD0ptS1Q</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/id3y8XD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fid3y8XD.jpg&h=40de114e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BP3rKv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBP3rKv2.jpg&h=1b11ad3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者：多年來中國在世界各地的外交機構都很安靜，很謹慎，為什麼最近很多中國大使開始積極發聲了？有人用&ldquo;戰狼&rdquo;來形容中國外交的輿論戰，您是&ldquo;戰狼&rdquo;嗎？<br />\n<br />\n中國駐意大利大使李軍華：中國人的基因是崇尚以和為貴，講求&ldquo;人敬一尺，我還一丈&rdquo;。因此，中國外交始終倡導相互尊重，平等相待，合作共贏。遺憾的是，總有一些國家少數政客，團體對中國抱有偏見和敵意，近來更是變得疫情反復對華造謠抹黑，極盡污名化之能事。且不說中國人民為防控疫情造成的巨大犧牲，僅三年至4月，中國共出口口罩278億隻，防護服1.3億套，檢測試劑盒7341萬人份，呼吸機4.91萬台（大佬，呢D大部分你係賣比人又唔係送。而且好多係次貨），這為國際抗疫做出了重要貢獻。請問這些造謠抹黑，<span style=\"color: orange;\">對中國公平嗎？道德嗎？</span>中國外交官當然要把真相介紹給駐在國人和媒體，還原事實，講明道理。這既是為中國捍衛公平正義，也是為各自維護國際道義。<span style=\"color: orange;\">相信任何國家的我個人不認為&ldquo;戰狼&rdquo;是合適的標籤，&ldquo;功夫熊貓&rdquo;的比喻或許更貼切。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />熊貓瀕臨絕種wor，咁樣咒自己國家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=======<br />\n五毛睇死呢個channel訂閱人數冇可能過一萬。你可以幫幫手嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QunCLp8421g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQunCLp8421g&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=bd80fe67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QunCLp8421g</a>"},{"pid":"b5e5fe079797534c59732c5c0a96188fe9a5b6bd","tid":2031280,"uid":54721,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"Foodpanda"},{"pid":"4b21b06954b76929405fa38a20a4d5a998ebb8ad","tid":2031280,"uid":48040,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"b5e5fe079797534c59732c5c0a96188fe9a5b6bd","tid":2031280,"uid":54721,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"Foodpanda"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"中美脫鉤之後，可能真係全民送外賣"},{"pid":"bef1347b8efa691e41450af8889f52a8907a3a30","tid":2031280,"uid":302,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5h0h9gs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5h0h9gs.jpg&h=5e3e05a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMZbozy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMZbozy.png&h=c2502554&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35507765987d9e8b3d4aba8201f3413bdcca92d9","tid":2031280,"uid":48040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bef1347b8efa691e41450af8889f52a8907a3a30","tid":2031280,"uid":302,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5h0h9gs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5h0h9gs.jpg&h=5e3e05a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMZbozy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMZbozy.png&h=c2502554&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"幫你推一推"},{"pid":"ded32a4019841b6b460385172d91639ec949b4d8","tid":2031280,"uid":1